author: More Perfect Union
description:
Jeff Yass—a billionaire TikTok investor and the 25th richest person in the world—is trying to buy PA’s Supreme Court.

The outcome of the race could flip the makeup of the court and affect how it decides on voting rights, abortion rights, and more.
title: This Billionaire TikTok Investor is Trying to Buy a Critical Election | ft. Jessica Burbank
